Definition: a visual presentation showing how something works
Example: the lecture was accompanied by dramatic demonstrations; the lecturer shot off a pistol as a demonstration of the startle response
Synonyms: verb, perception, demonstrate, demo, visual_communication, a, visual, presentation, showing, how, something, works, the, lecture, was, accompanied, by, dramatic, demonstrations, lecturer, shot, off, pistol, as, of, startle, response
Category: noun.communication
